title: Full Stack Developer
description: We are seeking a talented Full Stack Developer to join our dynamic team. The ideal candidate will have experience in both front-end and back-end development, with a solid understanding of web technologies, databases, and UI/UX design principles. You will work on building and maintaining web applications, ensuring they are robust, scalable, and user-friendly. Proficiency in MERN stack, Django, and PHP is a plus. Join us to contribute to exciting projects and grow your skills in a collaborative environment.
requirements: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and frameworks like React or Angular.
Experience with server-side languages and frameworks such as Node.js, Django, or PHP.
Familiarity with both relational databases (e.g., MySQL, PostgreSQL) and NoSQL databases (e.g., MongoDB).
Experience with Git and collaborative workflows.
Ability to work well in a team and communicate effectively.

title: Backend Developer
description: Looking for a skilled Backend Developer to work remotely. The candidate should have experience with server-side technologies and databases. Proficiency in Node.js and Python is essential.
requirements: Strong understanding of Node.js and Python.
Experience with SQL and NoSQL databases.
Knowledge of RESTful APIs.
Good problem-solving skills.
Ability to work independently and in a team.

title: Frontend Developer
description: Join our team as a Frontend Developer. The ideal candidate should have a keen eye for design and a strong understanding of web technologies, especially React.
requirements: Proficiency in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and React.
Experience with responsive design and cross-browser compatibility.
Knowledge of UI/UX design principles.
Experience with Git.
Strong communication skills.

title: Database Administrator
description: We are looking for a part-time Database Administrator. The candidate should have experience in managing both SQL and NoSQL databases.
requirements: Experience with database administration.
Strong knowledge of MySQL and MongoDB.
Ability to troubleshoot database issues.
Experience with backup and recovery procedures.
Good communication skills.

title: Full Stack Developer

requirements: Experience with full stack development.
Proficiency in JavaScript, Python, and Django.
Knowledge of healthcare industry standards is a plus.
Strong problem-solving skills.

title: Mobile App Developer
description: Seeking a talented Mobile App Developer with experience in React Native or Flutter. The candidate will work on developing cross-platform mobile applications.
requirements: Experience with mobile app development.
Proficiency in React Native or Flutter.
Knowledge of mobile UI/UX design principles.
Experience with RESTful APIs.
Ability to work in a team.

title: Data Scientist
description: We are looking for a Data Scientist to join our remote team. The candidate should have experience in data analysis and machine learning, especially in the medical field.
requirements: Strong background in data science.
Experience with Python, R, and SQL.
Knowledge of machine learning algorithms.
Experience in the medical field is a plus.
Strong analytical skills.

title: System Administrator
description: Seeking a part-time System Administrator to manage our IT infrastructure. The candidate should have experience with network and server management.
requirements: Experience in system administration.
Knowledge of network protocols and security.
Experience with Windows and Linux servers.
Good problem-solving skills.
Ability to work independently.

requirements: Proficiency in React and JavaScript.
Experience with responsive design.
